headline: Marriott International Again Named One of Fortune's World's Most Admired Companies
summary: Marriott International today announced it has once again been named one of Fortune'sWorld's Most Admired Companies. The company has appeared on Fortune's Most Admired Companies' list consecutively since its inception in 1998. Marriott was named number one in the Hotels, Casinos, and Resorts category and placed number 14 in this year's ranking overall.
